text: Dušan Macháček (born 7 October 1966) is a Czech rower. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Prague
